* `convex_Icc (r s : ℚ) : Convex ℚ (Set.Icc r s)` (`Mathlib/Analysis/Convex/Basic.lean`).
* `convexOn_of_slope_mono_adjacent` / `convexOn_iff_slope_mono_adjacent`
